# Grimverse Validation Rule

Validate before generation.

## Required checks
- Shot has valid scene link
- Scene has valid episode link
- Character references resolve by id, stem, or alias
- State node exists for active characters
- Status is from the approved schema
- Completed shots have image_source and video_source
- Asset source paths resolve to existing files when provided
- Template placeholders such as `${tp.user.sceneId}` are ignored in template files only

## Failure behavior
- Stop and report critical issues
- Do not auto-correct canon silently
- Suggest the smallest safe fix

## Execution note
If the vault includes `03_SYSTEM/validate_vault.py`, treat it as the authoritative executable checker for batch audits.
